name: Jordan 1 Retro High Neutral Grey Hyper Crimson
description: Ditching the conventional all-leather design of the silhouette, a mixed-material construction features the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Neutral Grey.' Soft gray suede overlays contrast a folded black leather foundation with Hyper Crimson's contrasting pop on the suede collar. ' SP 19 Air Jordan 1 High OG ' on the quarter panel is stamped in black print.
